      <text>*a proclamation, sent to all the nobility, with rumors spread among others*
High Ladies, High Lords, Ladies, Lords, and Members of the Blood,
Greetings from the Empress, may she live forever.
Because of the recent captures of a number of Oathbreakers in the
Westlands, the Empress, may she live forever, has, in her infinite grace,
announced that there will be an auction, that all may participate in, to
purchase these prisoners as covale.  This auction is to be held in the
capital city, Seandar, where the Empress, may she live forever, has 
declared that she herself may make an appearance.  This auction is to 
take place over the course of the next few months, as there have been 
so many captured that it will be impossible to hold it in one day.  There
will be a festival to accompany.
The Empress, may she live forever, looks forward to this event, and to 
seeing her subjects gathered together.

*sealed with the mark of the Empress*

*OOC: This is going to be the event in which Davien will be sold.  Due
to circumstances, this is going to be a sort of timewarped event, to 
take place ICly approximately 3 months from this point.  This is to allow
all of you plenty of time to reach Seandar from whatever parts of the world
you happen to be in.  Obviously, this will be near the end of the 
festival event.  The day of the auction in which Davien will be sold 
will be Friday, March 7th, at 8:00 pm EST.  If this is not a good time,
well, send me a message.   Further details on the OOC board about how this
auction is to work.*
</text>
